cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper deals with image analysis and machine learning techniques for cell counting, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The proposed method involves domain adaptation, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. Additionally, the use of a density regression model is related to neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
